<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Boston Scientific cut.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Boston Scientific cut.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Cowen &amp; Co said it reduced the rating on Boston Scientific Corp to buy from strong buy.</p>
<p>-- shares fell 12-3/4 to 47-3/4.</p>
<p>-- company said on Thursday it expected first quarter earnings to be significantly below the consensus estimate of $0.47 per share, citing revenues hurt by currency fluctuations.</p>
